    "constitutionalAuthorityStatementText": "<pre>\n[Congressional Record Volume 172, Number 43 (Monday, March 9, 2026)]\n[House]\nFrom the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href=\"https://www.gpo.gov\">www.gpo.gov</a>]\nBy Mr. BENTZ:\nH.R. 7862.\nCongress has the power to enact this legislation pursuant\nto the following:\nThis bill amends the National Flood Insurance Act of 1968\nto limit the application of the Endangered Species Act with\nrespect to certain actions under the national flood insurance\nprogram.\n[Page H2476]\n</pre>",
